  _NPCName: Sunny
  _lines:
  - Hello Moony!!!
  - What is that you have there-!
  - Beignets??
  - Ohhhh those look so good!!
  - Thank you Moony
  - :)
  - 'Hehe, I''m glad you like them '
  - 'Howie made them '
  - 'I had another gift for you '
  - But it got swept up by some creature when I was waking up
  - I'm sorry Sunny
  - 'It was really cute too, I''ll make sure to look for them again a little later '
  - But for now lets got on with our date, hm?
  - 'I love you '
